				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183469" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;" >Zyn</a></span> <span class="odate time_1514855976 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Jan 2018 01:19</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3671562">
									

<p>Big thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514857908" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3208919); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1514857908" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3208919); return false;">taylor_itkin</a></span> for reading this over in chat, and also all the people who posted in the discussion page for <a href="/scp-723-j">SCP-723-J</a> with suggestions for the rest of the -ad Roach family, and pretty much everyone in chat who joked with me about said -ad Roach family. Thanks to all of that, this page now exists, as does this: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/kiryu-labs-roach-wrangling-log">http://www.scp-wiki.net/kiryu-labs-roach-wrangling-log</a></p>
<p>In all honesty, yes, this is silly. I wrote this a few months ago when it occurred to me that there wasn't a lot of stuff on the mainsite explaining how/why joke SCPs exist in-universe (if they do). My headcanon is that in-universe, researchers write those things up for fun, and so each lab/department has their own set of inside jokes because <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">according to my research</span> that's how nerds make friends.</p>
<p>ETA: all images are CC-compliant since I took them with my phone. I saw a couple roaches last summer.</p>
<p>Happy New Year everyone.</p>

							</div>

								
