			<div class="content" id="post-content-3672087">
									

<p>In the end, this page more or less boils down to this</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-723-J-# is a <em>Periplaneta Americana</em> (American cockroach) believed to be a relative to SCP-723-J.</p>
<p>SCP-723-J-#'s anomaly manifests as a pun.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SCP-723-J-# Intake Log Interview</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>Dr. ██████:</strong> SCP-723-J-#, did you do your thing again?</p>
<p><strong>SCP-723-J-#:</strong> [does thing]</p>
<p><strong>Dr. ██████:</strong> <em>Oh you</em></p>
<p><strong>SCP-723-J-#:</strong> [does thing again]</p>
<p><strong>Dr. ██████:</strong> Isn't this humorous? I'm talking to a cockroach, <em>and it's not talking back!</em> How wacky!</p>
<p><strong>SCP-723-J-#:</strong> [Continues to do thing]</p>
<p><strong>Dr. ██████:</strong> no.</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>It worked for fad roach, but overstayed its welcome after that. -1 for the lack of variety in the humor presented in what is ostensibly supposed to be a joke/humorous tale.</p>

							</div>

